      "author": "levid",
      "description": "HangarX v1.0.33\n\n## Highlights since the last release\n- Streaming agent chat with phase-pill animation, sub-agent rendering, and replay link\n- Skill packs (vault-qa, obsidian-chat, multi-hop) with tunable bounds\n- Multi-provider web search (OpenAI / Anthropic / Gemini native) with Perplexity fallback\n- Local cron / schedules dashboard\n- Settings IA refresh: 5 task-oriented sections, status badges, progressive disclosure, search filter\n- Diagnostics & overrides — clearer \"default ok\" / \"auto\" / \"ignored in local mode\" pills\n\nSee repo CHANGELOG for the full list.",
